@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@userId = user_123
@stripeCustomerId = cus_xxx
@stripeConnectId = acct_xxx

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Service Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Seed Test Balance (dev only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/balance/seed?amount=1000

### Onboard Runner
POST {{baseUrl}}/runners/onboard
Content-Type: application/json

{
