### Create Payment
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{userId}}",
  "customer_id": "{{stripeCustomerId}}",
  "amount": 50.00
}

### Create Transfer
POST {{baseUrl}}/transfers/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{userId}}",
  "destination_account_id": "{{stripeConnectId}}",
  "amount": 45.00,
  "description": "Delivery payout"
}

### Create Refund
POST {{baseUrl}}/refunds/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{userId}}",
  "payment_intent_id": "pi_xxx",
  "amount": 50.00
}

### Get Transactions by User
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/{{userId}}
